        Delivers the DeviceEntityDescription for an entity associated with a given OID.

        oid - the OID for which the corresponding description is to be returned
        Returns:
        the DeviceEntityDescription for the entity corresponding to the managed object identified by oid, or null if there is no entry.

      • getContainingEntityClass

        Class<? extends DeviceEntity> getContainingEntityClass(String oidValue)
        Deliver the class of the database entity that contains an element with a specified oid value
        Parameters:
        oidValue - the value of the OID to be checked
        Returns:
        the class which contains a field with the specified oid. If oidValue refers to a table entry, the class of the parent table will be returned. If oidValue refers to a scalar, the class of the parent entity will be returned. Otherwise, the entity associated with the specified oid is returned.

      • getClassToOidMap

        Map<Class<? extends DeviceEntity>,org.snmp4j.smi.OID> getClassToOidMap()
        Lookup to deliver the OID for a given device entity.
        Returns:
        Map containing all entities for this device type.
